	<description>
		<p>Dave Gnukem is an open source retro-style 2D scrolling platform shooter, inspired by and similar to Duke Nukem 1. It currently runs on Windows, macOS, Linux and various other platforms. It is written in C++ using SDL library and it features an integrated level editor as well. This game is not really a clone or remake, it is probably most akin to a parody.</p>
	</description>
